    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The default selection is based on the selected index. You can change the default index by modifying how InstantSearch.js is initialized:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst search = instantsearch({\r\n  appId: 'latency',\r\n  apiKey: '6be0576ff61c053d5f9a3225e2a90f76',\r\n  indexName: 'instant_search', // << HERE\r\n  searchParameters: {\r\n    hitsPerPage: 8,\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou can change the index here: https://codesandbox.io/embed/vy4prppwmy\r\n\r\nDoes that solve your problelm @egyprotech ?",
